1
00:00:14,675 --> 00:00:20,113
<i>Connecting old words</i>
<i>that have been used up</i>

2
00:00:20,948 --> 00:00:28,855
<i>I just want to convey</i>
<i>my simple thoughts</i>

3
00:00:28,923 --> 00:00:34,293
<i>That day's faint wind blows away</i>

4
00:00:34,361 --> 00:00:38,422
<i>at the castle ruins of yesterday</i>

5
00:00:39,667 --> 00:00:44,570
<i>I'll laugh with you</i>
<i>and live for the moment</i>

6
00:00:45,306 --> 00:00:52,212
<i>Still that incident</i>
<i>will continue to trouble you, right?</i>

7
00:00:53,614 --> 00:00:57,106
<i>That's why it must be good bye</i>

8
00:00:57,184 --> 00:01:04,147
<i>Leaving nothing behind,</i>
<i>let us share what is left</i>

9
00:01:04,225 --> 00:01:11,290
<i>In time, we'll realize</i>
<i>that it was everything</i>

10
00:01:11,365 --> 00:01:18,032
<i>And sadness will touch our cheeks,</i>
<i>creating a river of tears</i>

11
00:01:18,506 --> 00:01:28,006
<i>Trembling thoughts swept into a vortex</i>
<i>and melting away</i>

12
00:01:45,911 --> 00:01:46,707
<i>Sasuke!</i>

13
00:02:00,192 --> 00:02:03,992
It will be necessary for you
to die once...

14
00:02:06,298 --> 00:02:08,061
Die once, you said?

15
00:02:18,476 --> 00:02:19,704
Mind Awakening Pill.

16
00:02:21,079 --> 00:02:22,774
You will take these.

17
00:02:23,381 --> 00:02:26,680
Mind Awakening Pill...?
What is that?

18
00:02:27,752 --> 00:02:30,778
Your Curse Mark level is
at the first state...

19
00:02:31,423 --> 00:02:32,981
These pills will forcibly stimulate

20
00:02:33,058 --> 00:02:35,856
the power of the Curse Marks
to the second state.

21
00:02:38,430 --> 00:02:40,864
However, if you move up
to the second state,

22
00:02:40,932 --> 00:02:44,197
the Curse Mark's erosion
will accelerate drastically

23
00:02:44,803 --> 00:02:47,294
and if things are left that way
you will die immediately!

24
00:02:49,074 --> 00:02:49,733
However...

25
00:02:50,609 --> 00:02:53,772
In order to control
the power of the second state,

26
00:02:54,079 --> 00:02:56,070
it is necessary to allow one's body
to get accustomed to it

27
00:02:56,147 --> 00:02:57,842
over the course of several hours.

28
00:03:01,319 --> 00:03:03,879
In doing so, you will...

29
00:03:04,256 --> 00:03:08,818
attain power that is
equal to ours, however...

30
00:03:10,929 --> 00:03:13,557
Once awake, you can't possibly
last more than a few minutes...

31
00:03:14,065 --> 00:03:15,657
and will certainly die!

32
00:03:16,701 --> 00:03:22,503
<i>Sound vs. Leaf</i>

33
00:03:38,523 --> 00:03:41,515
Die... and what will happen after that?

34
00:03:42,260 --> 00:03:44,091
You don't need to worry.

35
00:03:45,463 --> 00:03:47,693
That's why we're here.

36
00:03:54,172 --> 00:03:58,108
We will use Barrier Ninjutsu
to suppress the side effects.

37
00:03:59,044 --> 00:04:00,443
We will mitigate that phase

38
00:04:00,512 --> 00:04:03,504
to ease you from eternal death
to a state of half death.

39
00:04:07,385 --> 00:04:12,015
You really think I can put my faith
in your Barrier Ninjutsu or whatever?

40
00:04:12,791 --> 00:04:14,349
Master Sasuke...

41
00:04:15,293 --> 00:04:19,320
We normally function
as Lord Orochimaru's bodyguards!

42
00:04:19,831 --> 00:04:22,391
We know our stuff when it comes
to Barrier or Defense Ninjutsu,

43
00:04:22,467 --> 00:04:24,901
Curse Marks and Sealing Jutsu!

44
00:04:38,750 --> 00:04:43,483
<i>I absolutely cannot die yet!</i>

45
00:04:47,592 --> 00:04:48,559
I'm counting on you.

46
00:05:14,185 --> 00:05:14,776
Hey!

47
00:05:15,320 --> 00:05:18,346
We're gonna lose him
if you guys are slow!

48
00:05:32,303 --> 00:05:33,235
Get into position!

49
00:05:34,973 --> 00:05:35,940
Begin!

50
00:05:58,897 --> 00:06:00,057
- Four Black Mists Formation!
- Four Black Mists Formation!

51
00:06:18,650 --> 00:06:20,015
Black Seal!

52
00:06:24,889 --> 00:06:27,221
All right. We're done for now.

53
00:06:37,001 --> 00:06:38,798
Man, I'm exhausted.

54
00:06:39,137 --> 00:06:42,004
I didn't think this mission
would drag on this long.

55
00:06:49,414 --> 00:06:53,009
I'll go check out the situation.
Let's go, Raido!

56
00:06:53,651 --> 00:06:54,379
Right.

57
00:07:03,027 --> 00:07:05,587
Darn. This has sure gotten troublesome.

58
00:07:06,297 --> 00:07:07,389
There's one...

59
00:07:08,032 --> 00:07:09,090
No, two of them.

60
00:07:11,169 --> 00:07:12,033
Here they come!

61
00:07:23,715 --> 00:07:25,706
You guys are Orochimaru's...

62
00:07:26,784 --> 00:07:28,251
Judging from the direction
you came from,

63
00:07:28,319 --> 00:07:31,720
it appears that you are on your way back
from the Village Hidden in the Leaves...

64
00:07:39,063 --> 00:07:40,860
What's in that barrel?

65
00:07:41,933 --> 00:07:43,833
Having two Jonin as opponents...

66
00:07:44,936 --> 00:07:46,699
That's a tough one.

67
00:08:28,313 --> 00:08:30,508
<i>Every one of them</i>
<i>got the Curse Marks...</i>

68
00:08:31,182 --> 00:08:33,116
You refuse to answer?

69
00:08:33,785 --> 00:08:36,720
This will be different from that time before
with your surprise attack.

70
00:08:37,155 --> 00:08:38,645
Shut up, you scum!

71
00:08:38,890 --> 00:08:40,118
Just drop dead!

72
00:08:42,226 --> 00:08:43,887
Orochimaru's toys...

73
00:08:45,129 --> 00:08:47,359
Don't you dare monkey around
with Leaf Shinobi!

74
00:09:06,951 --> 00:09:09,010
Those two are really late, aren't they?

75
00:09:10,488 --> 00:09:12,456
What should we do, Shizune?

76
00:09:14,092 --> 00:09:14,990
Let's go see!

77
00:09:15,059 --> 00:09:15,650
Right!

78
00:09:24,402 --> 00:09:25,198
Shikamaru!

79
00:09:26,471 --> 00:09:27,301
What's the matter?

80
00:09:28,172 --> 00:09:31,471
There's a smell of blood nearby.

81
00:09:45,289 --> 00:09:46,881
Wh-What's this?!

82
00:10:01,806 --> 00:10:03,034
Raido! Genma!

83
00:10:14,152 --> 00:10:14,982
<i>This isn't good!</i>

84
00:10:23,327 --> 00:10:26,558
I can't believe these two
could have been taken down...!

85
00:10:42,680 --> 00:10:45,808
<i>The best I can do right now is</i>
<i>give him some stop gap treatment...</i>

86
00:10:46,384 --> 00:10:47,351
Shizune...

87
00:10:49,087 --> 00:10:51,248
I'm gonna hunt those guys down!

88
00:10:51,823 --> 00:10:52,551
No!

89
00:10:52,957 --> 00:10:54,322
B-But...

90
00:10:54,592 --> 00:10:57,925
W-Wait... Iwashi.

91
00:11:00,331 --> 00:11:04,791
Th-The Jutsu that those guys have
is no longer that of mere Shinobi...

92
00:11:07,038 --> 00:11:10,838
If you pursue them alone,
you'll only die.

93
00:11:12,343 --> 00:11:14,868
Genma... don't talk anymore!

94
00:11:25,456 --> 00:11:29,950
The smell of the other two impinged
on the five others including Sasuke...

95
00:11:31,062 --> 00:11:33,690
But the five are moving away
from the smell of the blood!

96
00:11:33,931 --> 00:11:34,727
What should we do?!

97
00:11:35,500 --> 00:11:39,129
Just as I thought.
He has guides.

98
00:11:40,037 --> 00:11:42,198
<i>This has really turned into</i>
<i>a real pain in the neck.</i>

99
00:11:42,573 --> 00:11:45,337
Let's hurry up and pursue Sasuke!

100
00:11:45,576 --> 00:11:47,168
Shut up, Naruto!

101
00:11:47,845 --> 00:11:51,838
That's for Shikamaru to decide!
Don't play the boss!

102
00:11:53,117 --> 00:11:54,049
Shikamaru?

103
00:11:55,319 --> 00:11:58,220
The fact that there was
the smell of blood probably means

104
00:11:58,589 --> 00:12:00,454
that a battle occurred somewhere.

105
00:12:01,125 --> 00:12:04,754
If we go to that location we should
be able to gather some information...

106
00:12:07,899 --> 00:12:09,730
We must be attentive
as we near the location,

107
00:12:09,801 --> 00:12:11,530
so we would have to switch over to

108
00:12:11,602 --> 00:12:14,036
a reconnaissance pattern
and approach walking slowly...

109
00:12:14,505 --> 00:12:16,871
While all that's going on

110
00:12:16,941 --> 00:12:19,034
Sasuke will cross over
the Land of Fire border!

111
00:12:19,911 --> 00:12:21,936
What are we gonna do, Shikamaru?!

112
00:12:28,586 --> 00:12:30,281
All right! Let's pursue Sasuke!

113
00:12:30,621 --> 00:12:33,215
All right! That's what I was waiting for!

114
00:12:33,891 --> 00:12:34,823
However...

115
00:12:37,562 --> 00:12:41,965
The fact that there was a battle
means they'll have their guard up.

116
00:12:42,667 --> 00:12:43,531
They'll certainly be aware

117
00:12:43,601 --> 00:12:45,728
of the fact that there might
be Ninja on their tail.

118
00:12:47,839 --> 00:12:48,965
In other words,

119
00:12:49,040 --> 00:12:51,634
the odds are high that
there will be traps or an ambush.

120
00:12:54,078 --> 00:12:55,272
Listen carefully...

121
00:12:55,346 --> 00:12:57,814
Hereafter, I want you to use your visual
and acoustic senses to the fullest!

122
00:12:58,216 --> 00:13:01,777
We need to locate those guys before
we get caught in an ambush!

123
00:13:02,753 --> 00:13:05,654
And if we come across
anything suspicious,

124
00:13:05,723 --> 00:13:08,715
don't just dodge them,
interpret them!

125
00:13:09,560 --> 00:13:10,720
All right!

126
00:13:10,862 --> 00:13:12,056
When we find them,

127
00:13:12,129 --> 00:13:14,825
I'm gonna use my new Jutsu
to clobber them!

128
00:13:15,433 --> 00:13:16,798
<i>That Naruto...</i>

129
00:13:17,001 --> 00:13:20,027
<i>Each time I see him</i>
<i>he's added a new Jutsu to his arsenal.</i>

130
00:13:20,571 --> 00:13:23,699
<i>Darn! Just when I thought</i>
<i>I had caught up with him...</i>

131
00:13:28,079 --> 00:13:30,172
Hey! The enemy's smell is everywhere!

132
00:13:30,615 --> 00:13:31,707
Everybody! Stop!

133
00:13:35,019 --> 00:13:36,509
Take a careful look above you.

134
00:13:40,625 --> 00:13:41,649
Paper Bombs...

135
00:13:42,727 --> 00:13:44,126
And in five other places too!

136
00:13:45,363 --> 00:13:47,558
The figuration is that of
a Perimeter Barrier.

137
00:13:48,466 --> 00:13:49,933
Perimeter Barrier?

138
00:13:50,668 --> 00:13:52,602
It's one type of Booby Trap Ninjutsu!

139
00:13:53,771 --> 00:13:57,172
Perimeter-type traps have a time lag
and are activated

140
00:13:57,241 --> 00:14:01,507
when one enters the area that
has been marked by the enemy.

141
00:14:02,780 --> 00:14:04,645
It's advanced Jutsu...

142
00:14:04,715 --> 00:14:07,115
It was in one of the books that
my father made me read.

143
00:14:10,221 --> 00:14:13,088
Darn! Our only choice
is to make a detour...

144
00:14:38,716 --> 00:14:42,550
<i>Lee... Do what you have to do!</i>

145
00:14:57,034 --> 00:14:57,659
Lee!

146
00:14:57,735 --> 00:14:59,225
It's too soon to be doing that!

147
00:15:00,371 --> 00:15:01,395
Lady Fifth Hokage!

148
00:15:01,939 --> 00:15:04,464
I already know that
you're a foolhardy guy.

149
00:15:05,609 --> 00:15:08,043
But you've just had an operation.

150
00:15:09,146 --> 00:15:10,807
You don't need to be rushing
into things.

151
00:15:20,091 --> 00:15:23,254
I want to hurry up and
do even a little training.

152
00:15:23,995 --> 00:15:26,122
I also want to... I want to...

153
00:15:27,198 --> 00:15:30,224
Building your strength isn't
the only form of training

154
00:15:31,202 --> 00:15:32,294
Don't you agree?

155
00:15:34,705 --> 00:15:36,400
It is said that Ninja are those

156
00:15:36,474 --> 00:15:39,375
who can forebear and
endure any hardship.

157
00:15:40,711 --> 00:15:41,871
I understand how you feel but...

158
00:15:42,747 --> 00:15:44,942
That means that this too
is one kind of training.

159
00:15:47,585 --> 00:15:48,643
Training...

160
00:15:49,687 --> 00:15:52,952
What if you were to do something foolhardy
and you got worse?

161
00:15:56,460 --> 00:15:58,360
Wh-What's that?

162
00:15:59,897 --> 00:16:02,161
It's medicine that I prepared.

163
00:16:02,600 --> 00:16:04,761
First, drink this and get better!

164
00:16:08,873 --> 00:16:09,737
Right!

165
00:16:10,207 --> 00:16:11,435
Come, let's go...

166
00:16:11,642 --> 00:16:12,438
Yes, ma'am.

167
00:16:17,882 --> 00:16:20,874
Damn! Nothing but traps!

168
00:16:21,018 --> 00:16:23,953
Yeah, but the enemy seems
pressed for time.

169
00:16:24,855 --> 00:16:26,550
The traps have noticeable flaws.

170
00:16:31,362 --> 00:16:34,854
Hey, hey, Naruto!
There's wire at your feet!

171
00:16:35,232 --> 00:16:36,529
Don't trip on it!

172
00:16:37,134 --> 00:16:38,567
I know that already!

173
00:16:39,970 --> 00:16:41,130
Wait, Naruto!

174
00:16:54,685 --> 00:16:56,277
Shadow Possession Jutsu...

175
00:16:57,154 --> 00:17:00,146
M-Made it just in the nick of time.

176
00:17:00,825 --> 00:17:03,919
Naruto! I told you to be careful!

177
00:17:06,797 --> 00:17:12,463
I see... One of the wires is
readily visible because it reflects light.

178
00:17:13,170 --> 00:17:16,765
The other wire has been coated
with a matte green.

179
00:17:17,908 --> 00:17:20,001
So it's very difficult to see
with the naked eye.

180
00:17:21,212 --> 00:17:22,338
It's a double trap, huh.

181
00:17:23,781 --> 00:17:25,442
Despite the fact that
they're in a hurry,

182
00:17:25,516 --> 00:17:27,541
that's certainly an elaborate trap.

183
00:17:28,252 --> 00:17:29,276
Which means that...

184
00:17:30,421 --> 00:17:31,513
That they're at rest.

185
00:17:32,490 --> 00:17:36,051
Perhaps they got injured,
or that itself could be a trap...

186
00:17:38,195 --> 00:17:38,957
Byakugan!

187
00:17:48,472 --> 00:17:49,234
Caught'em!

188
00:17:49,940 --> 00:17:53,068
All right! All right!
I'll drag Sasuke back without fail!

189
00:17:53,344 --> 00:17:55,710
Naruto! Hate to tell you this,

190
00:17:55,779 --> 00:17:58,543
but I'm gonna demonstrate
my new Jutsu right here!

191
00:17:59,683 --> 00:18:00,615
Me too!

192
00:18:01,719 --> 00:18:02,913
Don't be so hasty.

193
00:18:03,654 --> 00:18:05,849
As soon as preparations have been made
to implement my strategy...

194
00:18:06,924 --> 00:18:08,755
we'll make direct contact
with the target!

195
00:18:26,243 --> 00:18:31,545
Darn! When we're in a hurry,
having to take a darn break...

196
00:18:33,050 --> 00:18:34,210
It can't be helped.

197
00:18:35,119 --> 00:18:38,316
When one fights at the second state,
one's body gets drained drastically.

198
00:18:39,156 --> 00:18:40,123
More than that,

199
00:18:40,191 --> 00:18:43,092
it's an ordeal not to be able
to use one's body for a while...

200
00:18:43,694 --> 00:18:46,822
It can't be helped with
two Jonin class guys as the opponents.

201
00:18:47,665 --> 00:18:50,031
If we act in moderation,
we'll be done in.

202
00:18:56,640 --> 00:18:57,265
Kiba...

203
00:18:57,875 --> 00:18:58,842
In that event,

204
00:18:58,909 --> 00:19:01,605
don't mess up the timing
of the Smoke Bombs.

205
00:19:01,879 --> 00:19:02,675
Got it!

206
00:19:03,814 --> 00:19:04,610
Now then...

207
00:19:05,015 --> 00:19:06,312
we'll split up into two teams.

208
00:19:06,850 --> 00:19:07,509
- Right!
- Okay!

209
00:20:07,811 --> 00:20:10,371
It looks like they haven't noticed us yet.

210
00:20:12,750 --> 00:20:14,775
Hey, Sasuke's not around.

211
00:20:17,788 --> 00:20:18,948
It appears that...

212
00:20:19,356 --> 00:20:20,983
He's inside that "coffin."

213
00:20:21,759 --> 00:20:22,953
Is he dead?!

214
00:20:24,094 --> 00:20:27,621
That barrel is secured with Barriers.
I can't see through it.

215
00:20:28,699 --> 00:20:31,293
I wouldn't think that the guys
who wanted Sasuke

216
00:20:31,402 --> 00:20:34,269
would kill him that easily.

217
00:20:37,207 --> 00:20:38,731
You might be right about that.

218
00:21:13,744 --> 00:21:20,843
<i>Once in a long while, once in a while</i>

219
00:21:20,984 --> 00:21:26,513
<i>The remnants of a person</i>
<i>broken by dreams</i>

220
00:21:26,690 --> 00:21:31,753
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

221
00:21:35,065 --> 00:21:42,062
<i>Clinging to the Divine,</i>
<i>clinging to Buddha</i>

222
00:21:42,139 --> 00:21:47,668
<i>The remnants of a person crying</i>

223
00:21:48,078 --> 00:21:51,639
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

224
00:21:53,317 --> 00:21:56,377
<i>Rendezvous with a happy dance circle</i>

225
00:21:56,453 --> 00:22:00,253
<i>This is my victory pose, round and around</i>
<i>(round around)</i>

226
00:22:00,591 --> 00:22:03,526
<i>Shake shake shake</i>
<i>Let's look</i>

227
00:22:03,594 --> 00:22:07,724
<i>With a bye bye rhythm that never ends</i>

228
00:22:16,907 --> 00:22:22,004
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

229
00:22:23,947 --> 00:22:27,212
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

230
00:22:27,618 --> 00:22:30,815
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

231
00:22:31,088 --> 00:22:35,081
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

232
00:22:38,829 --> 00:22:41,354
Gimme a break, Shikamaru!
You're not reliable in the least!

233
00:22:41,432 --> 00:22:42,524
And you still call yourself
a leader?!

234
00:22:42,599 --> 00:22:44,430
But this situation sure
is a problem.

235
00:22:44,501 --> 00:22:46,366
Leave this kind of thing to me.
It'll be a cinch.

236
00:22:46,437 --> 00:22:48,405
- I sure hope it will be.
- What do you mean by that?!

237
00:22:48,839 --> 00:22:50,363
It's too much of a hassle to explain.

238
00:22:50,441 --> 00:22:51,635
- Shut up, Akamaru!
- Shut up, Akamaru!

239
00:22:51,708 --> 00:22:53,767
What was that?!
Give'em some more, Akamaru!

240
00:22:55,145 --> 00:22:58,808
Well, if things come to this,
I'll use that special weapon, Rasengan!

241
00:22:59,049 --> 00:23:02,883
Next time: "Squad Mutiny:
Everything Falls Apart!"
